info.name: April Fools' Contest
info.additionalText:
This is our major competition for this academic year, sponsored by [St Andrews Mathematics Society](https://sums-sta.github.io).

 There will be prizes of £50, £20, £10 for the top three contestants. This contest is open to everyone to attend, but the prizes are only eligible for students in a Scottish University. You will need a github account to participate. If you are a student in a Scottish University, please [register](https://forms.office.com/e/6pxQRsZ4DX) before the start of the contest in order to be qualified for the prize, otherwise there is no need to fill in the form. 

 Please [follow our discord](https://discord.gg/8wTzq7Megd) for updates on the contest, and ask question.
